---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
	title="About"
	description="ML Engineer transitioning to AI Safety Research Engineering."
	eyebrow="About"
>
	<!-- Intro -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Motivation</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-6 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<p class="m-0 text-ink text-2xl font-semibold leading-tight">On Transformative AI: Why AI Safety?</p>
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">We are on an exponential curve of AI capability development, and its economic and societal impact will continue to grow rapidly. This is my current view, strongly supported by empirical evidence and technical understanding. I approach it with scientific interest and clear-eyed rationality — I am excited about the technologies that can be created and the problems that can be solved with the help of powerful AI, but I also clearly see the technical challenges of building powerful AI responsibly and the societal upheavals that may follow as this technology reshapes the world and its power structures.</p>
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">We don't know how to ensure that powerful AI systems are aligned with our values. Crucially, our current alignment techniques may not generalize to the critical cases involving AI systems at or above human intelligence. How do we ensure that powerful AI systems solve challenging problems in the world without pursuing misaligned goals — or reshaping the world in ways that disregard human values, especially when they have the capability to do so effectively?</p>
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">I think these are hard, real problems of high significance. I hope to make contributions that marginally shift the future toward worlds where capable AI systems exercise their power in ways humans recognize on reflection as good.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Research Focus -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Research Focus</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">I'm currently focusing on improving the mechanisms of AI Control and understanding scheming behaviors in AI systems. I also have a strong interest in white-box methods for understanding models' reasoning and decision-making processes.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Industry Background -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Industry Background</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">I have extensive experience building ML systems end-to-end — from early-stage startups where I designed and shipped ML products from the ground up to large engineering organizations where I improve shared ML infrastructure and tooling. I'm equally comfortable prototyping quickly and writing production-grade code, and I enjoy building systems that work reliably at scale.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Education & Certificates -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 border-b py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Education & Certificates</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-8 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">AWS Certified Machine Learning — Specialty</h3>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>Jul 2025</time></p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Full Stack Deep Learning Bootcamp</h3>
							<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">Berkeley, CA</p>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>Nov 2019</time></p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Galvanize Data Science Immersive</h3>
							<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">San Francisco, CA — 700+ hours of hands-on training in Python, Statistics, ML, and Data Processing</p>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>2017</time></p>
					</article>
					<article class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-1 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:items-start">
						<div class="lg:col-span-2">
							<h3 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">B.S. in Finance, with Distinction</h3>
							<p class="mt-1 text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600">Belarusian State Economic University</p>
						</div>
						<p class="text-xs 2xl:text-lg text-base-600 lg:ml-auto"><time>2010</time></p>
					</article>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Beyond Work -->
	<section>
		<div class="max-w-[90rem] mx-auto px-8">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 py-12 border-base-200">
				<div class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 lg:z-40 self-start">
					<h2 class="text-sm 2xl:text-xl text-base-900 font-bold uppercase">Beyond Work</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:col-span-2 max-w-2xl">
					<p class="m-0 text-muted text-base leading-relaxed">I discovered competitive programming through following how AI systems have been advancing in this domain — and quickly got hooked. I balance this with professional and life commitments, but my long-term aspiration is to become a "red" coder.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</PageLayout>
